# CI/CD

## Must
- "Run lint, type-check (if TS), and tests on PRs"
- "Block merges on failing checks"

## Should
- "Use Dependabot or similar to keep dependencies updated"
- "Run static application security testing (SAST) and dynamic application security testing (DAST) in the CI pipeline."
- "Generate and upload a Software Bill of Materials (SBOM) for each build (e.g., CycloneDX or SPDX)."
